@NODE Introduction
@{B}Introduction@{UB}

@{U}Description@{UU}

ConvertReko can convert PC version of Reko cardset to Amiga version.
The converted cardset can then be used on Klondike for Amiga.


@{U}Features@{UU}

- HAM-8 Reko cardset output.
- Gamma-correction.

@ENDNODE

